==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Depthless
<hw>Depth"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having no depth;
shallow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of measureless depth; unfathomable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In clouds of <qex>depthless</qex> night.</q>
<rj><qau>Francis.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Depucelate</ent>⟦br⟧
